{"tid":965850,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Microsoft: Edge is the best!!!","createTime":"2019-01-02T11:03:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T00:18:51.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bd385f3186ebe5ece44322b22e9e126770ead263","tid":965850,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T11:03:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/237469163395167/posts/562327687575978/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F237469163395167%2Fposts%2F562327687575978%2F&d=mQHFsxKfgzE2mw2WxC2sD26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=2abcc614\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/237469163395167/posts/562327687575978/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.xfastest.com/21703/microsoft-edge-is-the-best/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.xfastest.com%2F21703%2Fmicrosoft-edge-is-the-best%2F&d=mQHFsxKfgzE2mw2WxC2sD26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=4f1425ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.xfastest.com/21703/microsoft-edge-is-the-best/</a><br />\n<br />\n早前，有 Microsoft 團隊的前工程師指控，Google耍手段打擊 Edge，否則以 Notebook 播放影片的省電效能，早就遠超過 Chrome<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，而 Microsoft 最新報告又指出，Edge 的效能已經超過 Chrome 和 Firefox<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n雖然 Microsoft Edge 因為相容性和效能問題，宣佈未來將改用 Google Chromium 為核心。但最近又低調地拿出測試報告顯示在最新版本 Windows 10 上的效能，Edge  還是比 Chrome 及 Mozilla FIrefox來得強。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.xfast-hosting.com/2018/12/microsoft-internet-explorer-performance-test.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.xfast-hosting.com%2F2018%2F12%2Fmicrosoft-internet-explorer-performance-test.jpg&h=b53014b2&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"053cccea11a35689f0da8c88871c0abca78fcc1c","tid":965850,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T11:03:55.000Z","msg":"Microsoft Edge 部門以執行 Windows 10 十月更新 (1809, 17763 release) 相同規格 (Intel i5 2.4 GHz 處理器、8G記憶體) 的 Surface Book，在相同的電腦環境設定下，透過 Wi-Fi 串流播放 HTML5 影片，並以 Edge 18、Chrome 69 與 Firefox 63 在全螢幕模式下播放，直到電池耗盡為止，最後研究小組再分析執行時間及用電資料。<br />\n<br />\n測試結果顯示，搭載 Edge 的電腦跑了超過 16小時，Chrome 將近 13 小時，而 Firefox 則只有 8 小時多。使用 Edge 的系統電池續航力比 Chrome 多了 24%，比起 Firefox 更是多了 94%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://microsoftedge.github.io/videotest/2018-10/video.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmicrosoftedge.github.io%2Fvideotest%2F2018-10%2Fvideo.html&d=mQHFsxKfgzE2mw2WxC2sD26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=daa9b06a\" target=\"_blank\">https://microsoftedge.github.io/videotest/2018-10/video.html</a>"},{"pid":"12794087f57bb8210f270b29c08b056243648ea0","tid":965850,"uid":60622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T11:12:34.000Z","msg":"Wfc"},{"pid":"b495c2612a45254b98516c1575134adf4b5c97a1","tid":965850,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T11:15:58.000Z","msg":"Edge = Webkit + Microsoft 一大堆自己獨有嘅 spec<br />\n<br />\n屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d93d1dfc16a65de023292dad21af74f3e04613c0","tid":965850,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T11:57:22.000Z","msg":"關人撚事咩<br />\nChrome Downloader<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c33c543a2421585268c56944bef07c85997e055","tid":965850,"uid":195438,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T12:02:24.000Z","msg":"用過一排Edge，雖然最後用返Chrome，但其實Edge冇大問題，反正我又唔用插件，不過我都解釋唔到點解會用返Chrome"},{"pid":"b051284dd87f560f1f4a87486ddf651df2ce01f6","tid":965850,"uid":210638,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T12:07:15.000Z","msg":"我之前用開chrome，嫌佢太沒功能性，轉左firefox好耐<br />\n<br />\nedge我覺得係唔錯但功能性都係唔夠，有啲位各有特色，如果有一個瀏覽器包哂就好"},{"pid":"d00c8313f569b1eb4dbc1cfb14545f8732ef4eac","tid":965850,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,